                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Integrity in every engagement</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
